extends com.b2international.snowowl.core.events.DelegatingRequest<com.b2international.snowowl.core.domain.RepositoryContext,com.b2international.snowowl.core.domain.RepositoryContext,R>
    A subclass of DelegatingRequest that:
    • opens an index read transaction using Index;
    • executes the delegate with a RepositoryContext that allows access to Searcher from the read transaction.
